	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />uCON64 isn't very good at NES stuff. AFAIK to join a PRG and CHR file with uCON64, you'd need to make a fake Pasofami header file which is dumb. You'd be better off using the DOS tool COPY.
<br />
<br />copy /b file.prg + file.chr newfile.out

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


