		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For splitting I use a quick script (well, it's part of my header fixing/cleaning script) that reads the header, then splits the chr and prg into different strings. IIRC ucon64 can split a rom into pasofami format though, so using that is easy enough if you can't script something

		

		</td>
