	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Use Total Commander (Windows Commander)
<br />
<br />Reneme files with added 001, 002, 003 (or more if hou have more files) as extension and click mouse on first file to combine into one file (xxx.out)
<br />
<br />example:
<br />
<br />nesdemo.hdr -&gt; nesdemo.001
<br />nesdemo.prg -&gt; nesdemo.002
<br />nesdemo.chr -&gt; nesdemo.003
<br />and run first 001 file (click mouse on it) for make nesdemo.out (combined all three files) <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />
<br />
<br />Fast and easy  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />

		

		</td>
